+	/*
+	 * If the BT chip's bt_en pin is connected to a 3.3V power supply via
+	 * hardware and always stays high, driver cannot control the bt_en pin.
+	 * As a result, during SSR (SubSystem Restart), QCA_SSR_TRIGGERED and
